      <title>Vista 银行：我们希望成为通往非洲的门户</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-17/vista-bank-we-want-to-be-the-gateway-to-africa-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[非洲的 Vista Bank 将在法国开业，扩大两大洲之间的全球贸易机会。Vista Group Holding 董事长 Simon Tiemtore 向彭博社首席非洲通讯员 Jennifer Zabasajja on Horizo​​ns Middle East and Africa 讲述了选择法国作为其首个欧洲分行的原因。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-17/vista-bank-we-want-to-be-the-gateway-to-africa-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:49:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>K'Ombudo：阿联酋将帮助肯尼亚增强经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-17/k-ombudo-uae-deal-to-help-kenya-strengthen-economy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚和阿联酋签署了一项经济伙伴关系协议，旨在加强双方的贸易和投资。重点关注的行业包括农业、医疗保健、金融服务、科技和旅游业。肯尼亚贸易部首席秘书 Alfred K&#39;Ombudo 在 Horizo​​ns Middle East and Africa 上与彭博社首席非洲通讯员 Jennifer Zabasajja 谈论了这项协议的时机以及与阿联酋合作延伸至乌干达和南苏丹的铁路线。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-17/k-ombudo-uae-deal-to-help-kenya-strengthen-economy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:49:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国大使称印度必须削减关税才能保持竞争力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/india-must-cut-tariffs-if-it-wants-to-compete-ambassador-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将离任的美国驻印度大使表示，如果印度想在唐纳德·特朗普即将爆发的与中国的贸易战中获胜，“毫无疑问”印度需要削减高关税，以便与东南亚更有利于商业的竞争对手竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/india-must-cut-tariffs-if-it-wants-to-compete-ambassador-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:48:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员现在看好英国央行三次降息以提振陷入困境的英国债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pound-falls-as-weak-retail-data-deals-fresh-blow-to-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于零售销售数据弱于预期，支持英国央行采取更积极的宽松政策以提振疲弱的经济增长，英国交易员目前倾向于英国央行今年三次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pound-falls-as-weak-retail-data-deals-fresh-blow-to-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:45:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中菲石油钻探受阻 美国企业瞄准菲律宾项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-17/us-firms-eye-philippine-oil-gas-projects-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾能源部长拉斐尔·洛蒂拉表示，菲律宾的石油和天然气项目吸引了美国公司的兴趣，因为与北京的紧张关系阻碍了马尼拉对能源丰富的南海的勘探。他在“与哈斯琳达·阿明的洞察”节目中发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-17/us-firms-eye-philippine-oil-gas-projects-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:38:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称万科已为人民币债券偿还准备现金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/vanke-is-said-to-have-prepared-cash-for-yuan-bond-payment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，开发商万科企业股份有限公司即将到期的债务金额创下了历史新高。上周五，在公司债券和股票出现动荡之前，万科企业股份有限公司向一些债权人表示，公司已准备好足够的现金来偿还 1 月 27 日到期的 2.95% 人民币债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/vanke-is-said-to-have-prepared-cash-for-yuan-bond-payment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:14:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
